## Saturday Session

# Run Warmup [endurance]

- warmup 10min @Z1
- 4x:
  - run 1min @Z4
  - recover 1min @Z1
- rest 2min

# Chipper [mixed]

- for-time 25min:
  - run 400m
  - kettlebell swing 21rep @24kg
  - pull-up 15rep
  - run 400m
  - kettlebell swing 15rep @24kg
  - pull-up 12rep
  - run 400m
  - kettlebell swing 9rep @24kg
  - pull-up 9rep

- rest 3min

# Cooldown [endurance]

- cooldown 5min @Z1
- walk 5min @Z1

> Focus on deep breathing and bringing HR below 120bpm.
